<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.190821>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Onconeura cascatinha n. sp. A – B — male, hypopygium, A — detail of tergite IX, dorsal, B — tergite IX removed, sclerites hatched; left: ventral, right: dorsal view with gonostylus removed. C – E — pupal abdomen, C — dorsal view, D — ventral view, E — detail of posterior row of spines on tergite IV." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/190821/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.190822>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Onconeura japi n. sp. A – B — male, hypopygium, A — detail of tergite IX, dorsal, B — hypopygium, tergite IX removed, sclerites hatched; left: dorsal, right: ventral view with gonostylus removed. C – F — female genitalia, C — ventral view, left with gonapophysis removed, D — dorsal view, E — apodeme lobe, F — labia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/190822/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.190824>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Onconeura oncovolsella n. sp. A – C — male, A — wing, B — hypopygium, tergite IX removed, sclerites hatched, right: ventral view, with gonostylus removed, C — hypopygium, detail of tergite IX, gonocoxite and gonostylus, dorsal, D – G — female genitalia, D — dorsal view, E — ventral view, left with gonapophysis removed, F — apodeme lobe, G — labia, H — vaginal opening." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/190824/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.190826>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Onconeura similispina n. sp. A – C — male, A — wing, B — hypopygium, detail of tergite IX, dorsal, C — hypopygium, tergite IX removed, sclerites hatched; left: ventral view with gonostylus removed, right: dorsal view. D – G — female genitalia, D — dorsal view, E — ventral view, left with gonapophysis removed, F — apodeme lobe, G — labia, H — vaginal opening." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/190826/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

